events.name: Present and Future of Neurotechnologies
events.description: hey NeuroHackers, After the success of Neuross Demo Day @NTU, NeuroTechSG is proud to launch its very first national event focusing on the Commercial Opportunities in Neurotechnologies!  The agenda is as follows:  - Introduction to Singapore Futurists - Introduction to NeuroTechX & Hackers in Neurotechnology - Overview of Brain-Computer Interface & Commercial applications - Overview of Various Neurotechnology Projects- Demo of Starter Neurotechnology Projects (Neuross @NTU)- How can you get involved? Join us to learn more about neurotechnology, how you can get involved and what NeuroTechSG is all about! Many thanks to our great partner, Singapore Futurists, for powering this event!
events.location: IMDA PIXEL Labs@NDC,  111 Middle Road #03-04, National Design Centre, Singapore 188969
